name: Balance
description: Living in a confusing world. Have you ever been grateful for the existence of devils and angels? Imagine if in this world there were no devils and angels, what would we be now? Like the sun and the moon, devil and angels also balance our lives. Wouldn't it be boring if there were only good people without bad people? and conversely, wouldn't it be boring if there were only bad people without good people? So stay grateful.
